>Description:
when helpdesk searches "for Keyword, ..., or Text", the entire page
gets presented, unformatted, all underlined, rather than just the
neighborhood of the occurrence.
Searching for a primitive function easily leads to out-of-memory.
>How-To-Repeat:
in helpdesk, next to the search button, use the pulldown menu
to select "for Keyword, Index Entry, or Text".
Then search for, say, "improper".
